[0.016, "o", "Jun 07 11:14:00 arvdzy systemd[1]: Starting MariaDB 12.3.2 database server...\r\n\u001b[0;90m\u001b[0;38:5:245m░░ \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32mSubject: A start job for unit mariadb.service has begun execution\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;90m\u001b[0;38:5:245m░░\u001b[0m \u001b[0;32mDefined-By: systemd\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;90m\u001b[0;38:5:245m░░\u001b[0m \u001b[0;32mSupport: https://lists.freedesktop.org/mailman/listinfo/systemd-devel\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;90m\u001b[0;38:5:245m░░\u001b[0m \u001b[0;32m\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;90m\u001b[0;38:5:245m░░\u001b[0m \u001b[0;32mA start job for unit mariadb.service has begun execution.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;90m\u001b[0;38:5:245m░░\u001b[0m \u001b[0;32m\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;90m\u001b[0;38:5:245m░░\u001b[0m \u001b[0;32mThe job identifier is 1448.\u001b[0m\r\nJun 07 11:14:00 arvdzy (mariadbd)[1606]: \u001b[0;1;33m\u001b[0;1;38:5:185m\u001b[0;1;39m\u001b[0;1;33m\u001b[0;1;38:5:185mmariadb.service: Referenced but unset environment variable evaluates to an empty string: MYSQLD_OPTS, _WSREP_NEW_CLUSTER\u001b[0m\r\nJun 07 11:14:00 arvdzy mariadbd[1606]: 2026-06-07 11:14:00 0 [Note] Starting MariaDB 12.3.2-MariaDB source revision 9f98f82b14a9b939834281672b6d0cf965db69a3 server_uid vRfEqc7pu3UK+o4Dl5RGJrZa4sw= as process 1606\r\nJun 07 11:14:00 arvdzy mariadbd[1606]: 2026-06-07 11:14:00 0 [Note] InnoDB: The first data file './ibdata1' did not exist. A new tablespace will be created!\r\nJun 07 11:14:00 arvdzy mariadbd[1606]: 2026-06-07 11:14:00 0 [Note] InnoDB: Compressed tables use zlib 1.3.2\r\nJun 07 11:14:00 arvdzy mariadbd[1606]: 2026-06-07 11:14:00 0 [Note] InnoDB: Number of transaction pools: 1\r\nJun 07 11:14:00 arvdzy mariadbd[1606]: 2026-06-07 11:14:00 0 [Note] InnoDB: Using crc32 + pclmulqdq instructions\r\nJun 07 11:14:00 arvdzy mariadbd[1606]: 2026-06-07 11:14:00 0 [Warning] mariadbd: io_uring_queue_init() failed with EPERM: sysctl kernel.io_uring_disabled has the value 2, or 1 and the user of the process is not a member of sysctl kernel.io_uring_group. (see man 2 io_uring_setup).\r\nJun 07 11:14:00 arvdzy mariadbd[1606]: create_uring failed: falling back to libaio\r\nJun 07 11:14:00 arvdzy mariadbd[1606]: 2026-06-07 11:14:00 0 [Warning] InnoDB: native AIO failed: falling back to innodb_use_native_aio=OFF\r\nJun 07 11:14:00 arvdzy mariadbd[1606]: 2026-06-07 11:14:00 0 [Note] InnoDB: innodb_buffer_pool_size_max=8388612m, innodb_buffer_pool_size=128m\r\nJun 07 11:14:00 arvdzy mariadbd[1606]: 2026-06-07 11:14:00 0 [Note] InnoDB: Initialized memory pressure event listener\r\nJun 07 11:14:00 arvdzy mariadbd[1606]: 2026-06-07 11:14:00 0 [Note] InnoDB: Completed initialization of buffer pool\r\nJun 07 11:14:00 arvdzy mariadbd[1606]: 2026-06-07 11:14:00 0 [Note] InnoDB: Setting file './ibdata1' size to 12.000MiB. Physically writing the file full; Please wait ...\r\nJun 07 11:14:00 arvdzy mariadbd[1606]: 2026-06-07 11:14:00 0 [Note] InnoDB: File './ibdata1' size is now 12.000MiB.\r\nJun 07 11:14:00 arvdzy mariadbd[1606]: 2026-06-07 11:14:00 0 [Note] InnoDB: File system buffers for log disabled (block size=4096 bytes)\r\nJun 07 11:14:02 arvdzy mariadbd[1606]: 2026-06-07 11:14:02 0 [Note] InnoDB: Data file .//undo001 did not exist: new to be created\r\nJun 07 11:14:02 arvdzy mariadbd[1606]: 2026-06-07 11:14:02 0 [Note] InnoDB: Setting file .//undo001 size to 10.000MiB\r\nJun 07 11:14:02 arvdzy mariadbd[1606]: 2026-06-07 11:14:02 0 [Note] InnoDB: Database physically writes the file full: wait...\r\nJun 07 11:14:02 arvdzy mariadbd[1606]: 2026-06-07 11:14:02 0 [Note] InnoDB: Data file .//undo002 did not exist: new to be created\r\nJun 07 11:14:02 arvdzy mariadbd[1606]: 2026-06-07 11:14:02 0 [Note] InnoDB: Setting file .//undo002 size to 10.000MiB\r\nJun 07 11:14:02 arvdzy mariadbd[1606]: 2026-06-07 11:14:02 0 [Note] InnoDB: Database physically writes the file full: wait...\r\nJun 07 11:14:02 arvdzy mariadbd[1606]: 2026-06-07 11:14:02 0 [Note] InnoDB: Data file .//undo003 did not exist: new to be created\r