[0.001, "o", "\r\u001b[2d; https://php.net/ignore-user-abort\r\u001b[3d;ignore_user_abort = On\r\u001b[4d\u001b[K\u001b[5d; Determines the size of the realpath cache to be used by PHP. This value should\u001b[6;3H"]
[0.000, "o", "be increased on systems where PHP opens many files to reflect the quantity of\r\u001b[7d; the file operations performed.\u001b[8;3HNote: if open_basedir is set, the cache is disabled\u001b[9;3H"]
