[0.000, "o", "; Duration of time, in seconds for which to cache realpath information for a given\u001b[13;3H"]
[0.000, "o", "file or directory. For systems with rarely changing files, consider increasing this\u001b[14;3Hvalue.\u001b[K\u001b[15;3Hhttps://php.net/realpath-cache-ttl\r\u001b[16d;realpath_cache_ttl = 120\u001b[18;3HEnables or disables the circular reference collector.\u001b[19;3H"]
[0.000, "o", "https://php.net/zend.enable-gc\r\u001b[20dzend.enable_gc = On\u001b[K\r\u001b[21d"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[K\u001b[22d"]
[0.000, "o", "; If enabled, scripts may be written in encodings that are incompatible with\u001b[23;3H"]
[0.000, "o", "the scanner.  CP936, Big5, CP949 and Shift_JIS are the examples of such\u001b[24;3Hencodings.  To use this feature, mbstring \u001b[30m\u001b[43mextension\u001b[39;49m\u001b[m\u000f must be enabled.\r\u001b[25d;zend.multibyte = Off\u001b[K\r\u001b[26d\u001b[K\u001b[27d; Allows to set the default encoding for the scripts.  This value will be used\u001b[28;3Hunless \"declare(encoding=...)\" directive appears at the top of the script.\u001b[29;3H"]
[0.000, "o", "Only affects if zend.multibyte is set.\r\u001b[30d;zend.script_encoding =\u001b[K\r\u001b[31d\u001b[K\u001b[32d"]
[0.000, "o", "; Allows to include or exclude arguments from stack traces generated for exceptions.\u001b[33;3H"]
[0.000, "o", "In production, it is recommended to turn this setting on to prohibit the output\u001b[34;3H"]
[0.000, "o", "of sensitive information in stack traces\u001b[35;3H"]
[0.000, "o", "Default Value: Off\u001b[K\u001b[36;3H"]
[0.000, "o", "Development Value: Off\r\u001b[37d; Production Value: On\r\u001b[38d"]
[0.000, "o", "zend.exception_ignore_args = On\r\u001b[39d"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[K\u001b[40d;"]
[0.001, "o", " Allows setting the maximum string length in an argument of a stringified stack trace\u001b[41;3Hto a value between 0 and 1000000.\u001b[K\r\u001b[42d;"]
[0.000, "o", " This has no effect when zend.exception_ignore_args is enabled.\r\u001b[43d; Default Value: 15\u001b[44;3H"]
[0.000, "o", "Development Value: 15\u001b[K\r\u001b[45d; Production Value: 0\u001b[24;45H"]
